{"name":"动画","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/动画/","url":"/async/tags/动画.json","count":2,"_total":2,"_totalPage":1,"_page":1,"posts":[{"tags":[{"name":"Canvas","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/Canvas/","url":"/async/tags/Canvas.json","count":2},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":39},{"name":"动画","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/动画/","url":"/async/tags/动画.json","count":2},{"name":"游戏","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/游戏/","url":"/async/tags/游戏.json","count":2}],"categories":[{"name":"游戏开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/categories/游戏开发/","url":"/async/categories/游戏开发.json","count":1}],"url":"/async/posts/2015/04/18/learn-canvas-1.json","date":1429286400000,"path":{"year":2015,"month":4,"day":18,"name":"learn-canvas-1"},"subtitle":"Canvas动画学习系列","title":"前端动画对比","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/2015/04/18/learn-canvas-1/","content":"<p>将近三个月没写文章了，就在这三个月内，我从一只学生狗变成了上班族。现在一切都稳定下来了，决定重新开始写点东西了。以后的计划是每周一篇，努力坚持~</p>\n<p>之前玩了很长时间的Canvas动画，也写了一些工具和一些demo，放在了我Github上的<a href=\"https://github.com/LingyuCoder/learn-canvas\">learn-canvas</a>仓库里。在学习Canvas动画的过程中学到了不少宝贵的新知识，这篇主要是个人对于Canvas动画的一些想法以及与其他前端动画实现的一些对比。</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":35},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":29},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":39},{"name":"Kissy","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/Kissy/","url":"/async/tags/Kissy.json","count":1},{"name":"动画","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/动画/","url":"/async/tags/动画.json","count":2}],"categories":[{"name":"前端综合","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/categories/前端综合/","url":"/async/categories/前端综合.json","count":5}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/31/kissy-anime-plugin.json","date":1401465600000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":31,"name":"kissy-anime-plugin"},"subtitle":"一个小作业","title":"如何写一个KISSY动画插件","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/2014/05/31/kissy-anime-plugin/","content":"<p>最近写东西写的比较少，并不代表我一直在划水。之前阿里的前辈布置了三个作业，其中一个就是基于KISSY写一个动画插件。事实上，KISSY已经有自己的动画模块，叫做<a href=\"http://docs.kissyui.com/1.4/docs/html/api/anim/index.html\">anim</a>，这里前辈的意思就是让我再造一个轮子，<a href=\"http://lingyucoder.github.io/kissy-anime-plugin/\">DEMO页面</a>，<a href=\"https://github.com/LingyuCoder/kissy-anime-plugin\">Github页面</a></p>"}]}